WEBVTT

00:04:30.650 --> 00:04:32.339
Walikua wamedanganywa,

00:04:32.363 --> 00:04:33.872
wamedhulumiwa, wamepumbazwa,

00:04:33.896 --> 00:04:35.921
na nilienda kabisa pembeni yao.

00:04:36.659 --> 00:04:38.030
Nilisali sala zao,

00:04:38.054 --> 00:04:41.000
nilisalimika dhidi ya vishawishi
kadri ninavyoweza.

00:04:41.024 --> 00:04:43.444
Nilizamisha kichwa sio mara moja, ila
mara mbili

00:04:44.074 --> 00:04:46.439
kwenye dimbwi la ubatizo lililojaa kamasi.

00:04:46.463 --> 00:04:47.726
Niliamini.

00:04:49.355 --> 00:04:50.531
Sasa nini?

00:04:51.706 --> 00:04:54.821
Nilifika nyumbani kwa mda
kuwasha televisheni

00:04:54.845 --> 00:04:57.289
na kumwona Peter Jennings
akitangaza milenia mpya

00:04:57.313 --> 00:04:59.002
ilivyoingia duniani kote.

00:04:59.475 --> 00:05:03.841
Ikanijia kua ingekua
ajabu hata hivyo,